 R←Test_SetChanged_005(stopFlag batchFlag);⎕TRAP;projectName;projectPath;ref;result;list;ref2;ref3
⍝ Exercise the "SetChanged" command with the -recursive flag
 ⎕TRAP←(999 'C' '. ⍝ Deliberate error')(0 'N')

 R←T._Failed

 projectName←⊃⎕SI
 projectPath←∆PATH,'/',projectName
 #.⎕SHADOW projectName
 ref←⍎projectName #.⎕NS''

 :Trap (~stopFlag)/0
     result←∆RunUcmd'Createproject ',projectPath,' #.',projectName,' -keephistory=on'
 :Else
     →T.GoToTidyUp 1
 :EndTrap
 →T.GoToTidyUp result≢'#.',projectName

 ref2←⍎'Sub1'ref.⎕NS''
 ref3←⍎'Sub2'ref.⎕NS''
 ref3.⎕FX'r←Hello' 'r←''World'''
 ref3.vars←'# Markdown' '' 'APL is Great'
 result←∆RunUcmd'SetChanged #.',projectName,'.Sub1 -recursive'
 →T.GoToTidyUp 0=≢result

 →T.GoToTidyUp 3≠≢list←F.ListFiles projectPath,'\.acre\changes\'            ⍝ Because QuadVars is added due to the recursive option
 →T.GoToTidyUp 3≠≢list←'recursive'F.ListFiles projectPath,'\APLSource\'

 R←T._OK

∆TidyUp:
 F.RmDir projectPath
 ∆RunUcmd'CloseProject #.',projectName
⍝Done
